      "content": "Please stop worrying about what you *think* it is; sharp pain moving to the lower right side is a sign that needs immediate, professional attention, not just a quick fix. You should not mix codeine and ibuprofen without a doctor's explicit instruction, as that can be dangerous. For this kind of sudden, intense discomfort, you need to get to an urgent care center or emergency room right away.",
