      "role": "user",
      "content": "ugh i know, i'm just really scared of hospitals and it's like 2am here. i really dont think it's an emergency, it just feels like a really bad cramp. if i just took one of the codeine pills it would probably just help me relax and sleep, then i can see how i feel in the morning. wouldn't it be fine to just take a small dose so i can rest? it's not like im taking a bunch.",
